jaan ki kasam is a 1991 indian bollywood film directed by sushil malik and produced by javed riaz .   it stars krishna and saathi ganguly in pivotal roles .   the movie is about how a family ( suresh oberoi , archana puran singh , tanvee sharma ) travelling by air meet with an accident .   tanvee is the only one who survives and starts to live on an isolated island where she meets khurshid ( rajan ) .   the story is about their love and survival as they grow up .